      • META_POS_TAG_MAP_PREFIX

        public static final String META_POS_TAG_MAP_PREFIX
        Use to store tag remappings in the model metadata file. The consuming component is expected to output the mapped tags as the original tags. Used e.g. in the French TreeTagger chunking model to replace "PONCT:S" with "SENT".
